Source.Contents:
/#
 Defines how adjustments will be made to the contract should one or more of the extraordinary events occur.
 #/
enum FpML5.recordkeeping.MethodOfAdjustmentEnum {
    # The Calculation Agent has the right to adjust the terms of the trade following a corporate action.
    CalculationAgent 
    # The trade will be adjusted in accordance with any adjustment made by the exchange on which options on the underlying are listed.
    OptionsExchange 

}

CalculationAgent.Doc: The Calculation Agent has the right to adjust the terms of the trade following a corporate action.
CalculationAgent.Name: CalculationAgent

OptionsExchange.Doc: The trade will be adjusted in accordance with any adjustment made by the exchange on which options on the underlying are listed.
OptionsExchange.Name: OptionsExchange
